MyNovel is the best place to read stories for everyone. Here you can find any genre you like:

— love;
— fantasy;
— vampire/werewolf;
— crime;
— family and friendship. 

And so much more!

Our smart recommendation system will help you to find the right book and discover thousands of new similar ones. 
You can change research settings anytime and enjoy your favorite genre or just pick any story at random. 

MyNovel authors add high-quality content every day so that readers always have something new. We’re doing our best to make the app perfect for both readers and writers. 

We have a large MyNovel community where you can share your thoughts, ideas, guesses,  discuss it all not only with other readers, but also with authors and maybe even influence the narrative course. 

MyNovel team is working really hard to enroll as many writers as possible to bring the best quality content to you.

